00:52:04,455 --> 00:52:07,076
So basically, you talk about these freezes for creating,

1045
00:52:07,076 --> 00:52:09,138
for example, ground or pipes or similar.

1046
00:52:09,138 --> 00:52:11,639
And I assume creating a completely new type of freeze

1047
00:52:11,639 --> 00:52:12,660
requires some programming.

1048
00:52:12,660 --> 00:52:14,041
But I'm curious about the process.

1049
00:52:14,041 --> 00:52:15,702
If you have a freeze already, and you

1050
00:52:15,702 --> 00:52:17,663
want to adapt it to a new environment

1051
00:52:17,663 --> 00:52:21,446
with completely new art, what are the tools for doing that?

